original: Hallert, Nils Tore Eugen, tandläkare, Linköping, f. 4/7/12 i S. Sodberga, Jönköp. 1. G. 44 m. Margareta Johansson. Barn: Claes-Joel f. 45. — Stud:ex. i Linköp. 31, tandhkand. 33, tandl. 36. Prakt, i Linköp. ,sed. 37.
translated: Hallert, Nils Tore Eugen, dentist, Linköping, born on July 4th, 1912 in Södra Söderberga, Jönköping County. Married for the first time in 1944 to Margareta Johansson. They had one child, Claes-Joel, born in 1945. Nils passed his high school exam (stud:ex.) in Linköping in 1931, graduated from dental school in 1933, and became a licensed dentist in 1936. He began his professional practice in Linköping in 1937.
